Field Detail

MINIMUM_TEMP_BUFFER_LENGTH

public static final int MINIMUM_TEMP_BUFFER_LENGTH
This constants is used as safe minimum size for temporary buffer to pass to #writeTo method. It is actually set to quite a bit higher than strict minimum, just to give some room for expansion in case structure changes.
